betterquesting:10.desc:8:
§7§oPerform the ritual of the sleeper within the abyssal wasteland.

§fThe necronomicon is, well, evil... The rituals hold a lot of power, but the price you pay is a seemingly permanent scar in the fabric of my being. It feels wrong...
That said, corrupting my entire being at least got me closer to answers. Those that control my immortality are higher dimensional beings, existing in multiple 3D 'sections' of reality.
Thanks to these extremely evil, but extremely effective, powers, I've been able to open a portal that'll grant me access to more dimensions of space.
This evil, cursed, wasteland is impregnated with the magic that binds my undeath, I feel it in my bones...
